package example
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Action
    Represents selection, execution and recovering an action performed by an agent.
    CustomAgent
    CustomAgent class extends the jason.asSemantics.Agent class to provide custom agent behavior.
    Env
    The Env class represents the environment in which the agents of the system operate.
    PDDLGenerator
    The PDDLGenerator class is responsible for generating PDDL problem files based on given beliefs and predicates.
    Planner
    The Planner class represents an internal action for planning actions.
    RunPlanner
    The RunPlanner class provides functionality to run a planner and extract plan steps.
